name: 15nov2009
chorusText:
Kom ons loof die Heer
saam met die engeleskaar
Hy is in die hemel
en my hart is daar
O my siel wees bly, jou Verlosser is naby
En die hemelse kleed sal jy dra
Wees getrou en waak, hou jou klere rein
want die koms van die Here is naby
daar sal glorie wees in die hemel
in die heerlike lig van Sy aangesig

as my Jesus kom, HalleluJaH x2
Wonderful, wonderful Jesus is to me, 
Counselor, mighty God, Prince of peace is He
Saving me, keeping me, from all sin and shame 
Wonderful is my Redeemer, praise His Name
Rondom Jerusalem is berge		
so beskerm die Here Sy volk	    x2

Hy beskerm ons van agter en van voor af
So beskerm die Here Sy volk

Rondom Jerusalem is berge,
so beskerm die Here Sy volk
We are standing on Holy ground

We are standing on Holy ground
and I know that there 
are angels all around
Let’s  just praise Jesus now
for we are standing in His presence
on Holy ground
Let it rain, let it rain 
Open the flood gates of heaven
Let it rain, let it rain
open the flood gates of heaven
